fields.description: This presentation will show you how to install python in your computer or laptop, what are the IDE that you can install in order to write python' script. We will run a simple Hello-world program. in other words this workshop will be a must for our two weeks session on Learning python programming (May 2016)
fields.title: Getting started with Python

fields.description: We will meet 3 times during the first two weeks of May and you will learn how to program with Python. This will cover the basic of programming. If you want to have more information please send us an email
fields.title: Bootcamp : Learn how to program with Python
